name: NSItemProvider.ErrorCode
desc: The error codes that describe problems with consuming data from an item provider.

items.name: case itemUnavailableError
items.desc: An error code indicating that the requested data was unavailable from an item provider.

items.name: case unavailableCoercionError
items.desc: An error code indicating that the requested data type coercion is unavailable from an item provider.

items.name: case unexpectedValueClassError
items.desc: An error code indicating that type coercion to the requested class failed.

items.name: case unknownError
items.desc: An error code indicating an unknown error with consuming data from an item provider.
